title: The Receptive
reading: Your nature is open and grounding, capable of immense creation through support. You find strength in yielding and allowing possibilities to take root.

title: Splitting Apart
reading: A time of pruning and letting go of what no longer serves. Stability returns once the old foundation has been cleared.

title: Holding Together
reading: You are a magnet for connection, finding strength in shared purpose. Dedication to the collective brings lasting success.

title: Viewing
reading: You offer a higher vantage point, seeing patterns others miss. Observation before action is your path to wisdom.

title: Enthusiasm
reading: Your energy is infectious, sparking movement and inspiration in others. Like thunder, you announce the coming of something new.

title: The Opposing
reading: Conflict is not failure, but clarity in the making. Use differences in perspective to refine your own truth.

title: Obstruction
reading: A pause is not a stop; it is a time to gather strength. Turn inward and reflect before attempting the climb again.

title: Stagnation
reading: When flow stops, retreat into your own value. Do not force progress; wait for the natural cycle to turn.

title: Recovery
reading: After the dark, the light always returns. Small beginnings now gain momentum; cherish this fresh start.

title: Innocence
reading: Success comes when you act without guile or expectation. Trust your intuition and precise alignment with the moment.

title: The Well
reading: You are a deep resource for others, unchanging and essential. ensure your own depths are maintained so you can give freely.

title: Wind over Earth
reading: Growth comes from steady, consistent effort, like a tree rising. Do not rush; your rise is inevitable through persistence.

title: Following
reading: To lead, one must first know how to follow the flow of energy. Adapt to the times, and you will find your path.

title: Decaying
reading: What has spoiled requires attention and work to repair. Face the neglected parts of your life to restore vitality.

title: Excess
reading: The load is heavy, and the structure is stressed. You must move quickly and boldly to find a new balance.

title: Coming to Meet
reading: A sudden connection or idea presents itself. Be careful not to let this single element dominate your entire structure.

title: The Army
reading: Order and discipline are required for the task ahead. Organize your resources and lead with a centered mind.

title: Mountain over Earth
reading: True strength lies in reducing self-importance. By lowering yourself, you create a foundation that lasts.

title: Water over Earth
reading: You seek to bring people together. Like water seeking its level, you find the common ground where connection thrives.

title: Wind over Earth
reading: The wind blows everywhere, seeing all. Take a step back to view the whole picture before making your next move.

title: Thunder over Earth
reading: Music and energy rise from the earth. You have the power to create a rhythm that others will naturally want to follow.

title: Fire over Lake
reading: Fire and water clash to create steam and change. It is time to shed old skins and embrace a necessary transformation.

title: Water over Mountain
reading: Movement is difficult; obstacles lie ahead. Retreat to higher ground and seek advice rather than pushing forward blindly.

title: Heaven over Earth
reading: Heaven and Earth move apart. Do not seek external rewards now; cultivate your inner worth until the time is right.

title: Earth over Thunder
reading: The darkness is passing. A single line of light returns at the bottom. Listen to the small voice of hope; it is growing.

title: Mountain over Thunder
reading: Pay attention to what you take in and what you say. Like the mouth, you determine the quality of your own energy.

title: Water over Thunder
reading: Chaos reigns at the beginning. Do not despair; sorting the threads now will lead to great order later.

title: Wind over Thunder
reading: Stability comes not from standing still, but from moving with the rhythm. Consistency is your superpower.

title: Thunder over Thunder
reading: A sudden jolt brings clarity. Do not fear the noise; use the adrenaline to wake up and sharpen your focus.

title: Fire over Thunder
reading: There is an obstruction that must be bitten through. Energetic action is required to enforce justice and clear the path.

title: Lake over Thunder
reading: Joy follows movement. Put aside your ego and follow what feels right and true, regardless of precedence.

title: Heaven over Thunder
reading: Action without ulterior motive brings supreme success. Be natural, like the lightning that strikes without planning.

title: Earth over Water
reading: Water gathers under the earth. You have hidden potential and resources. Store them up; you will need them soon.

title: Mountain over Water
reading: A spring flows at the foot of a mountain. Learning is dangerous but necessary. Respect the teacher and the process.

title: Water over Water
reading: Danger upon danger. Do not struggle against the current; flow with it. Only by remaining calm will you survive the depth.

title: Wind over Water
reading: The wind blows over the water, dissolving foam. It is time to let go of rigid structures and clear away misunderstandings.

title: Thunder over Water
reading: The storm breaks and tension is released. Forgive, forget, and move forward. The obstacle has been cleared.

title: Fire over Water
reading: Fire moves up, water moves down. Compromise is impossible right now; verify your position and seek a neutral judge.

title: Lake over Water
reading: The lake has dried up. You are running on empty. Stop giving out and allow yourself to be replenished.

title: Heaven over Water
reading: Strength faces the abyss. Proceed with caution. Just because you can fight does not mean you should.

title: Earth over Wind
reading: Wood grows upward from the earth. Success comes from small, almost invisible improvements made every single day.

title: Mountain over Wind
reading: The air around the mountain is still. Correct the mistakes of the past to ensure a stable future.

title: Water over Wind
reading: The well is vital but the rope is short. You have the resource, but you must improve your method of reaching it.

title: Wind over Wind
reading: Like the wind, be pervasive and constant. Subtle influence is more powerful than brute force right now.

title: Thunder over Wind
reading: Thunder and wind stabilize each other. Find your routine, your rhythm, and stick to it. Endurance is the key.

title: Fire over Wind
reading: Warmth within the home. Focus on your inner circle and your defined role. Stability starts from the inside out.

title: Lake over Wind
reading: The beam is sagging under the weight. You have taken on too much. Move quickly to reinforce your life before it breaks.

title: Heaven over Wind
reading: The powerful prince meets a new element. Do not marry the first idea you see; exercise discretion.

title: Earth over Heaven
reading: Heaven flows beneath the Earth. perfect balance. Small effort yields great fruit. Enjoy this time of harmony.

title: Mountain over Heaven
reading: Heaven is held within the Mountain. You have a vast potential energy. Hold it back, refine it, and wait for the perfect moment.

title: Water over Heaven
reading: Clouds rise up to Heaven, but no rain yet. Enjoy the meal and the company while you wait. The rain will come in its own time.

title: Wind over Heaven
reading: The wind blows across the sky. You cannot force the outcome, but you can refine the details. Focus on the small things.

title: Thunder over Heaven
reading: Thunder rolls in the high sky. Use your power to embrace justice and act decisively. You are in a position of strength.

title: Fire over Heaven
reading: The sun shines in the center of the sky. Clarity and abundance are yours. Use this light to illuminate the goodness in others.

title: Lake over Heaven
reading: The dam is full. Tension is at its peak. State your truth openly and resolutely, but without violence. The break is coming.

title: Heaven over Heaven
reading: Pure, unadulterated creative power. You are the dragon flying in the sky. Create, lead, and inspire.

title: Earth over Lake
reading: The earth promotes the lake. Good things are approaching. Be generous and welcoming, for the harvest is near.

title: Mountain over Lake
reading: The lake evaporates to bless the mountain. Give up something now to gain something greater later. Sacrifice is holy.

title: Water over Lake
reading: The lake is full. Set boundaries. Unlimited freedom brings chaos; correct limits bring freedom to create.

title: Wind over Lake
reading: The wind blows over the lake, creating ripples. Verify the truth within yourself. If you are centered, you can influence even the stubborn.

title: Thunder over Lake
reading: Events are out of your control. You are entering a situation where you are not in charge. Accept your role and learn.

title: Fire over Lake
reading: Fire and Water pull apart. Acknowledging differences is the only way to coexist right now. Do not force unity.

title: Lake over Lake
reading: A lake rests upon a lake. Shared joy and conversation. Join with friends for discussion and practice. Happiness spreads.

title: Heaven over Lake
reading: The lake rises to the sky. A decision must be made to break through a deadlock. Be firm and remove what does not belong.
